    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_530210">Seeing how much coin you make while leveling gives you an idea of what coin is worth. Combine that with a man who makes a living on not just playing games but doing so better than 99% of players.  He is not some newb that doesn't understand game mechanics.<br />
<br />
The cooking thing was just as obvious as the miss priced cultural weapons, there is a reason people were cooking thousands of them.<br />
<br />
The reddit thread on the weapon exploit banning was hilarious. Anet posted basically &quot;If you think we did wrong post your account id and we'll tell you how many you bought&quot;  That shut up a lot of people, the ones that did have the balls to give their account id bought 200-1k of them.  People will cry and bitch when they think they can get away with it. &quot;I didn't know making 100 times more gold than I did leveling to 80 in a few minutes from practically no karma points was an exploit!&quot;  But when the truth comes out they get quiet real fast.<br />
<br />
Anet did unban some that contacted them and promised to delete all the stuff they bought.</div>
