People weren't banned for buying a single or a few of those cheap karma weapons for their personal use. They were banned for buying MASSIVE amounts of items just to sell them because they KNEW it wasn't going to last forever and they wanted to get the biggest benefit out of it before it gets fixed. THAT's what they got banned for.<br />
