    <td width="30" align="center" valign="middle"><img src="/forums/images/closeq.gif" width="30" height="30" align="right"></td>
  </tr>
</table>
</div>Why should I have to report anything in a game I'm playing for enjoyment.  I'm not being paid to fix the game's problems, in fact, I paid them to play the game.  The developers should not expect me to do their jobs for them, nor should players feel negative pressure to report bugs.</div>
